QueryText: Query on how to obtained Kisan Credit Card.

QueryText: Query about Management of diseases of Ginger
KCCAns: Recommended to Spray Mancozeb or Carbendazim @ 3g/lt of water

QueryText: Management of soft rot in Ginger
KCCAns: I suggest him spray Bavistin @ 2 gram per litre of water.
